{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Adriana Babakanian","author":"Adriana Babakanian"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"/Users/adrianababakanian/Code/gatsby-starter-blog/src/pages/prototyping/drawing-machine/index.md absPath of file >>> MarkdownRemark","html":"<p>I made this drawing machine as an extension of a simple rack-and-gear prototype I made to practice designing and piecing together gears from Illustrator files. I ended up laser cutting a small pen holder and attaching the prototype to a DC motor to get the device shown below, and then decided to turn it into a drawing machine that operates by using a photoresistor.</p>\n<video width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" autoplay loop muted>\n  <source src=\"/intro-8439cb2385c86426a1a6e8613cc52407.m4v\">\n  Your browser does not support the video tag.\n</video>\n<p>All components in this drawing machine were laser cut from Illustrator files I created. The circular turntable holds the drawing surface in place, the arm at then end of the rack holds a drawing instrument, and the acrylic box encases the electronics. I chose to make the electronics box out of acrylic since I designed the circuitry such that the drawing arm is contolled by a photoresistor.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/side-6393d41aca870379d207f49d57e9ba08-285f8.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Side\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/side-6393d41aca870379d207f49d57e9ba08-fb8a0.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/side-6393d41aca870379d207f49d57e9ba08-1a291.png 148w,\n/static/side-6393d41aca870379d207f49d57e9ba08-2bc4a.png 295w,\n/static/side-6393d41aca870379d207f49d57e9ba08-fb8a0.png 590w,\n/static/side-6393d41aca870379d207f49d57e9ba08-526de.png 885w,\n/static/side-6393d41aca870379d207f49d57e9ba08-fa2eb.png 1180w,\n/static/side-6393d41aca870379d207f49d57e9ba08-08f6a.png 1770w,\n/static/side-6393d41aca870379d207f49d57e9ba08-285f8.png 4032w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/gears-f5f8651e47fe07b19cda78f1b84423c7-285f8.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Gears\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/gears-f5f8651e47fe07b19cda78f1b84423c7-fb8a0.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/gears-f5f8651e47fe07b19cda78f1b84423c7-1a291.png 148w,\n/static/gears-f5f8651e47fe07b19cda78f1b84423c7-2bc4a.png 295w,\n/static/gears-f5f8651e47fe07b19cda78f1b84423c7-fb8a0.png 590w,\n/static/gears-f5f8651e47fe07b19cda78f1b84423c7-526de.png 885w,\n/static/gears-f5f8651e47fe07b19cda78f1b84423c7-fa2eb.png 1180w,\n/static/gears-f5f8651e47fe07b19cda78f1b84423c7-08f6a.png 1770w,\n/static/gears-f5f8651e47fe07b19cda78f1b84423c7-285f8.png 4032w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>When light shines on the photoresistor, the motor is activated, thus turning the gear to move the pen at the end of the arm. In this way, the undulating circular patterns shown below are created.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/final-c6748eb9e1e3f0b840ff86ed967cf595-70380.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Final\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/final-c6748eb9e1e3f0b840ff86ed967cf595-fb8a0.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/final-c6748eb9e1e3f0b840ff86ed967cf595-1a291.png 148w,\n/static/final-c6748eb9e1e3f0b840ff86ed967cf595-2bc4a.png 295w,\n/static/final-c6748eb9e1e3f0b840ff86ed967cf595-fb8a0.png 590w,\n/static/final-c6748eb9e1e3f0b840ff86ed967cf595-526de.png 885w,\n/static/final-c6748eb9e1e3f0b840ff86ed967cf595-fa2eb.png 1180w,\n/static/final-c6748eb9e1e3f0b840ff86ed967cf595-08f6a.png 1770w,\n/static/final-c6748eb9e1e3f0b840ff86ed967cf595-70380.png 3264w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Circumferential Drawing Machine","date":"June 12, 2018"}}},"pathContext":{"slug":"/prototyping/drawing-machine/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/design/feaster/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Feaster"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/design/doodles/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Doodles"}}}}